%% Diagram: DataTransfer mode lifecycle
%% Type: stateDiagram
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> ReadWrite: dragstart fires
    ReadWrite: read/write mode
    ReadWrite: setData() OK
    ReadWrite: setDragImage() OK
    ReadWrite: effectAllowed OK

    ReadWrite --> Protected: dragstart returns
    Protected: protected mode
    Protected: types readable
    Protected: payloads hidden
    Protected: setData / getData ignored

    Protected --> Protected: drag / dragenter / dragover / dragleave
    Protected --> ReadOnly: drop fires
    Protected --> [*]: dragend with no drop

    ReadOnly: read-only mode
    ReadOnly: getData() OK
    ReadOnly: setData() ignored

    ReadOnly --> [*]: drop returns
